cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper is primarily focused on attacks against machine learning models, specifically neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses security and privacy concerns, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The experiments involve image classification, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the limitations of learning-based strategies, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
